text: :For the Swedish musician, see Daniel Håkansson Daniel Håkansson (born March 13, 1996) is a Swedish ice hockey player. He is currently playing with Linköpings HC of the Swedish Hockey League (SHL). Håkansson made his Swedish Hockey League debut playing with Linköpings HC during the 2014–15 SHL season. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1996 births Category:Living people Category:Linköping HC players Category:Swedish ice hockey forwards Category:People from Linköping
